folder: Humboldt Street & Ten Eyck Street, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Humboldt Street - Ten Eyck Street
text:
260-262 Humboldt Street, at the N.E. corner of Ten Eyck Street. Also seen is Ten Eyck Street, north side, to Bushwick Ave. Razed buildings are being replaced with new low rent apartments, under the Federal Housing Act. In the background, at the right, is seen St. Catherine's Hospital.

December 22, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
